description: Delicious vegan food is on the streets of OKC, courtesy of Mim's Bakery & Nosh! The proof is in the pudding, or should I say pie? No dairy, no eggs, no problem! The Mim's trolley serves a variety of entrees featuring fresh, local produce and artisan style trolley-made bread. And save room for dessert, because all the fantastic taste you want from your cookies, cakes, pies, and more are still here, and ready to satisfy you!
name: Mim's Bakery & Nosh
